    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Sites that are underwater and where archaeological excavations or exploration takes place. Included are shipwrecks, harbor and dock remains, fishing structures, and flooded land sites.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
